  <div class="m-hero-block__body">
    <header>
      
      <h4><a href="http:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.behindthesteelcurtain.com&#x2F;nfl-pittsburgh-steelers-news" class="plain nfl-pittsburgh-steelers-news">Latest News</a></h4>
        <h2><a href="http:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.behindthesteelcurtain.com&#x2F;nfl-pittsburgh-steelers-news&#x2F;2015&#x2F;2&#x2F;19&#x2F;8068683&#x2F;ryan-clark-retirement-twitter-instagram" data-analytics-link="hero">Fans and players react to Ryan Clark's retirement</a></h2>
  <p class="m-hero-block__byline ">
    <span class="byline meta-byline">by <a href="http://www.behindthesteelcurtain.com/authors/neal-coolong">Neal Coolong</a></span>
  </p>

    </header>

      <p class="m-hero-block__blurb">Fans and players took to Instagram and Twitter after ex-Steelers safety Ryan Clark announced his retirement from the NFL.</p>

