    </div>

    <h3><a href="http:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.behindthesteelcurtain.com&#x2F;pittsburgh-steelers-nfl-features-news-blog-long-form&#x2F;2015&#x2F;2&#x2F;18&#x2F;8062621&#x2F;steelers-2015-schedule-an-early-look-at-the-oakland-raiders" data-analytics-link="river">Steelers 2015 Schedule: Previewing the Raiders</a></h3>
  </header>

    <div class="m-block__body__byline">
    by <a href="http://www.sbnation.com/users/Jeff.Hartman">Jeff.Hartman</a>
  Feb 18, 2015, 1:58p
  <span class="m-entry-admin-button " data-remote-admin-entry-type="button" data-remote-admin-entry-id="7826662"></span>

</div>



    <p class="m-block__body__blurb">The Pittsburgh Steelers&#x27; schedule is difficult, but there are certainly games where they should be heavily favored. One of those game will be when the Oakland Raiders travel to Heinz Field in 2015.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      </div>
    </div></div>

