    <h3><a href="http:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.behindthesteelcurtain.com&#x2F;pittsburgh-steelers-opinions-reactions-news-updates&#x2F;2015&#x2F;2&#x2F;18&#x2F;8062251&#x2F;the-nfl-combine-is-this-weekend-and-its-important-apparently" data-analytics-link="river">Trying hard to get excited for the Combine</a></h3>
  </header>

    <div class="m-block__body__byline">
